{"tid":638206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地男假金鏈騙財　儀器難測真偽","createTime":"2018-04-22T13:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T17:08:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8189b1d269de5e408c4c7b17b0e0579f7afd6c","tid":638206,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:46:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180422/20369059?_ga=2.116117126.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369059%3F_ga%3D2.116117126.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=rwHfFTi%2BbPbufjMtzjzA%2BqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=13ed8b42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369059%3F_ga%3D2.116117126.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=d568fcd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180422/20369059?_ga=2.116117126.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月22日 <br />\n<br />\n內地男假金鏈騙財　儀器難測真偽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180422/large/a1003a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180422%2Flarge%2Fa1003a.gif&h=71f51cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正所謂真金不怕洪爐火，但內地一名曾經營金店生意男子，以金包銀的「高仿」14K黃金頸鏈（圖）行騙，就連儀器也沒法測出真假。他涉嫌利用這種高仿假黃金頸鏈詐騙全國多間典當店舖，在過去5年於全國各地犯案10多宗，直至近日才被江蘇鹽城警方將他拘捕，並予刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5年內多間當舖中招<br />\n<br />\n據悉，鹽城市警方本月13日晚在鹽城大豐區一間賓館拘捕以高仿假黃金行騙的陳姓男子，當場搜出假黃金頸鏈一條。陳供稱，他以前是做打金店生意的，曾接觸到用金包銀做假黃金的渠道，後來生意虧本，他在周轉不靈時，就拿假黃金飾品到全國各地進行典當，因其行蹤不定，五年間一直沒有被抓到。但上月他在鹽城市區鹽馬路某典當行行騙，才被鹽城警方盯上。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，陳男在3月30日到典當行，向當值的王小姐表示，要將頸上戴的黃金頸鏈典當一個月。王小姐一看該男子50多歲，衣着考究，手錶、手包、腰帶都是名牌，很有老闆派頭，就先信了幾分。她將頸鏈進行水測密度法和火槍加熱等方法檢測，一切都符合黃金的特性。她故意壓低價表示只能當1.7萬元人民幣（下同，約2.1萬港元）」，但陳不同意，非要2萬元（近2.5萬港元）不可。王認為2萬仍有利可圖，收下了黃金頸鏈。到本月3日，該金鏈才被專家鑑定為是金包銀的假頸鏈。<br />\n<br />\n江蘇《現代快報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n台女騙兩港商逾千萬　判囚10個月<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n急流中練習　桂林龍舟翻側17死<br />\n<br />\n台女騙兩港商逾千萬　判囚10個月<br />\n<br />\n訛稱為雙親換心肝　實質買豪宅掃名牌美魔<br />\n女騙台商2,700萬"},{"pid":"d418aadfa4f9abad9436e9f25075e65bb9df2044","tid":638206,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:47:44.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\n唔可以用 archemedes principle 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0536c64004bcfbaf4550295111b2b0560ca80897","tid":638206,"uid":27530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d418aadfa4f9abad9436e9f25075e65bb9df2044","tid":638206,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:47:44.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\n唔可以用 archemedes principle 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T15:18:36.000Z","msg":"咁你下下有相同重量既金？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732ad73746fab269f77593f54490e5a2520612a0","tid":638206,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T15:21:05.000Z","msg":"正宗金鑲銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb7fd67eb5db7a4e05b64ba47ec0b5af9349790","tid":638206,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T15:24:28.000Z","msg":"真金不怕紅爐火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f0fa805b75eb8aea4f5d3e82d0b10f2ea76107","tid":638206,"uid":128210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T16:27:00.000Z","msg":"中。國。<br />\n只。有。騙。子。係真野。<br />\n其他就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e58dde95895a054dc15f387d60701da6c2fce8e","tid":638206,"uid":121130,"like":0,"disl